Welcome to Lands of Intrigue!

This server is based on an Open Source project found on the NWVault called Spellplague: The Rebirth, which itself is based on a June 2020 version of the old Knights of Noromath Persistent World.  Other than using the great work of the Spellplague team as a base, please note that the Development Team here has no affiliation with these other modules.

Characters on Lands of Intrigue start at level 3. All of your first three classes must be the same but afterward there are no restrictions.  3.5 Multiclassing rules do apply.  Make sure that you fully complete your levelup before proceeding.

In this room you will select a number of Customization Feats.  Pull one of the levers to begin this process.  Please note that some of these choices such as Class Standing and Background do affect some dialogue options with NPCs as well as mechanical opportunities in-game.  These choices represent your character before they arrive in Tethyr. Knowing your character concept you should have some idea of which selections fit best for them.


If for any reason you would like to view this text again, simply right click on the statue holding a sword in front of you and "Examine" it using the eye-ball button.



If you require additional help or would like to talk to us, the GM's, or your fellow players, you can find us on Discord: https://discord.gg/ZRgsBj48uC
